extends _template.pug

block title
  | Resources for journalism

block page
  h1 Resources for journalism

  div.boxes.grid.center
    div.box
      h2 Press kit
      p Download a package with images and other media, for use in articles reporting about us.
      p Download #[+dl('/static/download/press_kit.zip') press_kit.zip]

    div.box
      h2 Get free hardware for review
      p If you run a Youtube channel, podcast, website, or similar; and you want to review our devices, we will be very happy to send you some.
      p Check #[+a('blog/hardware_review') Get hardware for review] page.
